==English==
===Adjective===
'''disinterested'''
# having no [[stake]] in the [[outcome]], and being free of [[bias]]; [[impartial]]
# lacking interest; [[indifferent]]; [[apathetic]]

====Translations====
;impartial
*Swedish: [[ojävig]]

[[sv:disinterested]]
[[vi:disinterested]]
[[zh:disinterested]]

===Usage note===
According to some, only the sense of "impartial" is correct, but the term has come to be synonymous with [[uninterested]], or lacking interest.